txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Gilded sword sheaths from the goblins surrounding Tyrn Lhuig. Delivery of the items should be made to Othran at the base of the hilltop outpost.
'Goblins have no need of the sword sheaths that they use. Take their sheaths and deliver them to us.'
Council of the North Task: Gilded Sword Sheaths
The hunters at Tyrn Lhuig expect a delivery of gilded sword sheaths to be made to Othran, one of their number at the bottom of their hillside outpost.
Deliver the gilded sword sheaths to Othran at Tyrn Lhuig in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver gilded sword sheaths from the goblins surrounding Tyrn Lhuig to Othran at the bottom of the hillside outpost.
Wanted: Gilded sword sheaths from the goblins surrounding Tyrn Lhuig.
